<br>
Solo:<br>
1.  Highest Evo DD - Currently Cinder Bolt<br>
2.  Second Highest DD - Currently Blaze<br>
3.  Magic Based DD - Currently Shock of Spikes<br>
4.  Malaise or low level bolt to pull<br>
5.  Utility - Either pet when chaining, DS when not using Fire, or Nullify Magic when fighting casters<br>
6.  Best pet heal - Currently Renew Summoning<br>
7.  Swap - Buffs, summoning, 2nd pet heal, Burnout II<br>
8.  Gate<br>
<br>
Group:<br>
1.  Highest Evo DD<br>
2.  Second Highest DD<br>
3.  Magic Based DD<br>
4.  Malaise<br>
5.  Damage Shield<br>
6.  Highest Rain or Debuffer<br>
7.  Swap/Burnout<br>
8.  Gate <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showMessageRange?topicID=31.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a> <b>7</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showPrevMessage?topicID=31.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showNextMessage?topicID=31.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=122><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.threadControl?topicID=31.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=31.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrary